text.tspan: The More We Worship God for His Mercy
Worship of the Father — His Mercy
The more we worship God for His mercy,
The more we shall taste His sweetness;
The more we worship God for His mercy,
The more we shall gaze upon Him.
Lord, I thank You for Your rich mercy which flowed,
Reaching me even when I had strayed,
That I might live Christ in the church as Your bride.
I will praise! I will sing! O I’m blest!
I will praise! I will sing! O I’m blest!
